#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_texturelayered.rst:21
msgid ""
"Base class for :ref:`Texture2DArray <class_Texture2DArray>`, "
":ref:`Cubemap <class_Cubemap>` and :ref:`CubemapArray "
"<class_CubemapArray>`. Cannot be used directly, but contains all the "
"functions necessary for accessing the derived resource types. Data is set"
" on a per-layer basis. For :ref:`Texture2DArray <class_Texture2DArray>`\\"
" s, the layer specifies the array layer."
msgstr ""

